body_html:
Ah, I see.
But still, this looks like a GCC bug looking at your error message.

When I search the error message at google, I see some relevant issues, please make sure to check existing issues to see if these apply to you. It looks like this can be a memory problem. Also in stackoverflow I can see some recommended solutions.
tensorflow/serving#13
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36264339/tensorflow-serving-compile-error-using-docker-on-osx

body:
Ah,  I see.
But still, this looks like a GCC bug looking at your error message.

When I search the error message at google, I see some relevant issues, please make sure to check existing issues to see if these apply to you. It looks like this can be a memory problem. Also in stackoverflow I can see some recommended solutions.
https://github.com/tensorflow/serving/issues/13
